fm: string addStrings(string num1, string num2) {         int m = num1.size(), n = num2.size();         string longer, shorter;         if (m >= n) {             longer = num1;             shorter = num2;         } else {             longer = num2;             shorter = num1;             swap(m, n);         }         int carry = 0, i = 1;         while (i <= n) {             int sum = longer[m - i] - '0' + shorter[n - i] - '0' + carry;             carry = sum / 10;             sum %= 10;             longer[m - i] = sum + '0';             ++i;         }         while (carry) {             if (m - i < 0) {                 longer.insert(longer.begin(), '1');                 break;             }             int sum = longer[m - i] - '0' + carry;             carry = sum / 10;             sum %= 10;             longer[m - i] = sum + '0';             ++i;         }         return longer;     }

fm: bool canPartition(vector<int> &nums) {         int n = nums.size(), sum = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)             sum += nums[i];         if (sum % 2)             return false;         sort(nums.rbegin(),nums.rend());         return helper(nums, sum / 2, 0);     }

fm: int countBattleships(vector<vector<char>>& board) {         int m = board.size(), n = m == 0 ? 0 : board[0].size(), res = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < m; ++i)             for (int j = 0; j < n; ++j)                 if (board[i][j] == 'X' && (i + 1 == m ||  board[i + 1][j] == '.') && (j + 1 == n ||  board[i][j + 1] == '.'))                     ++res;         return res;     }

fm: vector<vector<int>> levelOrder(Node *root) {         vector<vector<int>> order;         if (!root)             return order;         queue<Node *> que;         que.push(root);         while (!que.empty()) {             vector<int> temp;             auto len = que.size();             for (int i = 0; i < len; ++i) {                 Node *currentNode = que.front();                 temp.push_back(currentNode->val);                 que.pop();                 for (auto child:currentNode->children)                     que.push(child);             }             order.push_back(temp);         }         return order;     }

Node *flatten(Node *head) {         if (!head)             return nullptr;         stack<Node *> s;         Node *root = head;         s.push(head);         while (!s.empty()) {             head = s.top();             s.pop();             if (head->next) s.push(head->next);             if (head->child) s.push(head->child);             head->child = nullptr;             if (!s.empty()) {                 head->next = s.top();                 s.top()->prev = head;             }         }         return root;     }
